notes.title: FInishing Touches
notes.details: This project was meant as a practice of material-ui while handling forms with formik and yup, while developing a feel for typescript. In my opinion, material-ui is best for making quick and clean professional looking websites. However, to go beyond clean and professional looking and to make a fully customized website, it is necessary to be good in css.
